ISLAMABAD, Jul 20 (APP): The father of Principal Information Officer (PIO) Mubasher Hassan , a senior officer of the Ministry of Information, has passed away.
His funeral prayer will be offered today at 2:00 p.m. at Board of Intermediate and Secondary Education Colony, Jamrud Road, Peshawar.
